    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-fda-osel",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the single-condition limitation does not invalidate the validation conclusion because the ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration is the regulatory standard for this device class and the primary failure mode of interest. All three QoIs satisfy pre-established quantitative acceptance bounds. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
